'''奧斯曼建築'''是[[奧斯曼帝國|奧斯曼帝國]]統治時期在帝國統治地區内流行的一種建筑風格<ref>{{cite news
 |url         = http://todayszaman.com/tz-web/detaylar.do?load=detay&link=151325
 |accessdate  = 2008-09-17
 |title       = Historian Kiel spends half century tracing history of Ottoman art
 |date        = 2008-08-27
 |work        = [[Today's_Zaman|Today's Zaman]]
 |first       = Mesut
 |last        = Çevikalp
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080912152015/http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/detaylar.do?load=detay&link=151325
 |archivedate = 2008-09-12
}}</ref>，發源于[[塞琉古帝国|塞琉古建築]]，受影響于[[拜占庭式建筑|拜占庭建築]]、[[馬木留克建築|馬木留克建築]]、[[亞美尼亞建築|亞美尼亞建築]]和[[伊朗建築|伊朗建築]]，成型于14到15世紀的[[布尔萨|布尔萨]]和[[埃迪爾內|埃迪爾內]]兩地<ref>''Seljuk architecture'', Illustrated Dictionary of Historic Architecture, ed. Cyril M. Harris, (Dover Publications, 1977), 485.</ref><ref>''Architecture(Muhammadan)'', H. Saladin, Encyclopaedia of Religion and Ethics, Vol.1, Ed. James Hastings and John Alexander, (Charles Scribner's son, 1908), 753.</ref><ref name=muqarnas12>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=RtbeBrAHhxgC&pg=PA60&lpg=PA60&dq=Ottoman+Architecture|title=Muqarnas: An Annual on Islamic Art and Architecture. Volume 12|last=Necipoğlu|first=Gülru|oclc=33228759|year=1995|publisher=Leiden : E.J. Brill|accessdate=2007-08-20|page=60|isbn=978-90-04-10314-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=INsmT6zjAl8C&pg=RA1-PA29&lpg=RA1-PA29&dq=Ottoman+Architecture|title=Islamic Architecture in Cairo: An Introduction|last=Behrens-Abouseif|first=Doris|isbn=90-04-08677-3 |year=1989|publisher=Leiden ; New York : E.J. Brill,|accessdate=2007-08-20 |page=29}}</ref><ref name=european>{{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com/?id=wgPSUQ873scC&pg=PA193&lpg=PA193&dq=Ottoman+Architecture |title=The Europeans: A Geography of People, Culture, and Environment|last1=Rice|first1=John Gordon|author2=Robert Clifford Ostergren|issn=0033-0124 |year=2005|journal=The Professional geographer|volume=57|issue=4|accessdate=2007-08-20|publisher=Guilford Press|isbn=978-0-89862-272-0}}</ref>。實際上，奧斯曼建築可以說是拜占庭建築的變體，有著巨大的圓形拱頂，注重内外設計的和諧統一。例如奧斯曼式的[[清真寺|清真寺]]建筑風格幾乎都是參照自[[聖索菲亞大教堂|聖索菲亞大教堂]]<ref name=european />，只不過奧斯曼建築在其基礎上融入了更多的中東地區的特色<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=Xu_L_FJRvUIC&pg=PA92&lpg=PA92&dq=Ottoman+Architecture |title=Muqarnas: An Annual on Islamic Art and Architecture. Volume 3|last=Grabar |first=Oleg |isbn=90-04-07611-5|year=1985 |publisher=Leiden : E.J. Brill,|pages= |accessdate=2007-08-20}}</ref>。

